							Specialized utilities for placental image analysis and processing, 
							developed for medical AI research applications.
						</p>
						<div class="tool-features">
							<h4>Key Features:</h4>
							<ul>
								<li>2D ultrasound image preprocessing</li>
								<li>Placental boundary detection</li>
								<li>Volume estimation algorithms</li>
								<li>Medical image enhancement</li>
								<li>DICOM format support</li>
